sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller as 调用方<br/>（REPL.tsx 等）
    participant State as bootstrap/state.ts
    participant Sub1 as 订阅者 1<br/>（concurrentSessions.ts）
    participant Sub2 as 订阅者 N<br/>（其他模块）

    Note over State: import 时<br/>const sessionSwitched = createSignal()
    Sub1->>State: onSessionSwitch(callback1)（注册订阅）
    Sub2->>State: onSessionSwitch(callbackN)（注册订阅）

    Caller->>State: switchSession(newId)
    Note over State: STATE.sessionId = newId
    State->>Sub1: sessionSwitched.emit(newId) → callback1(newId)
    State->>Sub2: sessionSwitched.emit(newId) → callbackN(newId)
